    "header_color": "green",
    "pages": [
      {
        "page": 1,
        "total_pages": 2,
        "content": [
          "English spelling is not logical.",
          "There is a long and rich history",
          "as to why, but the fact remains:",
          "the same letters can sound",
          "completely different.",
          "",
          "The most famous example is -ough.",
          "",
          "  through = 'oo'                Press 1",
          "  though  = 'oh'                Press 2",
          "  tough   = 'uff'               Press 3",
          "  thought = 'aw'                Press 4",
          "  cough   = 'off'               Press 5",
          "  bough   = 'ow'                Press 6",
          "",
          "Six words, six sounds, same four",
          "letters. That is English. There is",
          "no rule here, only familiarity."
        ],
