      {
        "page": 2,
        "total_pages": 2,
        "content": [
          "Some patterns do help when reading.",
          "",
          "Silent letters are everywhere. The k in",
          "know, the w in write, the b in doubt, the",
          "s in island. You just have to learn which",
          "letters stay quiet.",
          "",
          "Double letters usually make the vowel before",
          "them short. Compare diner with dinner.",
          "Hoping with hopping. The double letter",
          "changes the sound of the whole word.",
          "",
          "Every card in this cluster comes with a",
          "memory trick for the spelling. The tricks",
          "work. Trust them and they will stick."
